npc/warden: You found your way to me — most don't. The maze turns people in circles until they give up and leave.
npc/warden: There's a locked gate on the path ahead. I can't open it; the House keyed it and dropped the key somewhere off the safe route.
npc/warden: Follow the glowing line — it points to the key. Take it, come back, and the gate is yours.
npc/warden: And don't trust the shiny footing out there. The prettiest platforms are the ones built to drop you.
